1
00:00:00,680 --> 00:00:01,680
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

2
00:00:01,710 --> 00:00:02,710
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

3
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:18,180
[Love Upon a Time Series]

4
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:20,200
Whither do you think to escape me!!

5
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,060
- What is the matter?!
- I had a nightmare.

6
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:28,040
Tonight, might you share my bed?

7
00:00:31,120 --> 00:00:33,120
[Love Upon a Time Series]

8
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:46,880
[Love Upon a Time Series]

9
00:02:24,930 --> 00:02:27,220
Why is my heart beating faster
than it did in the nightmare?

10
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:48,730
You...

11
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:51,630
You want me to drink it?

12
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:13,640
Whoa!

13
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,680
It's so sweet.

14
00:03:15,170 --> 00:03:16,270
Palm wine.

15
00:03:16,850 --> 00:03:18,940
Fermented with palm sugar.

16
00:03:19,670 --> 00:03:20,690
Its effect is quite mild,

17
00:03:21,850 --> 00:03:23,240
ensuring that one
will not suffer a headache.

18
00:03:28,050 --> 00:03:28,840
Strange.

19
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:31,840
You're usually

20
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,840
pretty against me
drinking alcohol, aren't you?

21
00:03:35,380 --> 00:03:36,840
You have been troubled.

22
00:03:37,890 --> 00:03:39,540
Here with me,

23
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:41,840
no harm shall come to you.

24
00:03:44,170 --> 00:03:45,600
Drink just enough,

25
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,560
so that you may rest without dreams.

26
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,320
The reason Klao...

27
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:09,640
I mean, I

28
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,720
got into heavy drinking

29
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,640
might be because

30
00:04:15,660 --> 00:04:16,880
I wanted to sleep without dreaming.

31
00:04:33,650 --> 00:04:35,680
You must have been very troubled.

32
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:38,440
The nightmare you were having,

33
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:40,880
was it again related to your father?

34
00:04:53,130 --> 00:04:53,930
Yeah, kind of.

35
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:56,520
I...

36
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,320
I saw Cherd in my dream.

37
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,120
I saw him

38
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,280
trying to hurt me.

39
00:05:12,670 --> 00:05:14,240
When you fell ill before,

40
00:05:15,170 --> 00:05:18,640
I saw you plagued by a nightmare
in your sleep.

41
00:05:19,530 --> 00:05:21,250
I know this is painful for you,

42
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:25,200
but the more you dwell on
the truth about your father,

43
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:28,080
the greater the toll it takes
on your mind and body.

44
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:31,920
I worry for you greatly.

45
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:41,140
Leave the past behind,

46
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,520
and let me be the one to fill your present

47
00:05:45,400 --> 00:05:47,000
with joy without end.

48
00:05:58,290 --> 00:05:59,060
Come on!

49
00:05:59,550 --> 00:06:00,620
You freaking microwave.

50
00:06:02,840 --> 00:06:03,730
No,

51
00:06:04,250 --> 00:06:06,860
in this era, he's more like

52
00:06:08,490 --> 00:06:09,710
a charcoal stove.

53
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,930
Stop it!

54
00:06:14,430 --> 00:06:15,450
Don't get too invested now.

55
00:06:16,030 --> 00:06:17,140
The one he cares about is Klao,

56
00:06:17,410 --> 00:06:18,840
not you, Nakun.

57
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,230
May I

58
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:31,660
ask you something, Phop?

59
00:06:34,330 --> 00:06:35,159
Are you...

60
00:06:35,880 --> 00:06:37,440
more worried about me

61
00:06:38,260 --> 00:06:38,940
or

62
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,060
Klao, the one you knew?

63
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:47,800
What is it you are implying?

64
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,720
I mean...

65
00:06:58,210 --> 00:07:00,020
I'm not the real Klao.

66
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,230
This is your chance, Nakun.

67
00:07:02,730 --> 00:07:03,960
It's time to tell him the truth.

68
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:19,080
You are Klao,
the one I once knew, are you not?

69
00:07:34,030 --> 00:07:35,840
Though you speak strangely

70
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:38,550
and act somewhat recklessly,

71
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,800
unlike your former self,

72
00:07:42,940 --> 00:07:45,440
and though
I sometimes see you smile and laugh,

73
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:48,880
my concern for you remains unchanged.

74
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:09,560
I believe you know in your heart
well enough

75
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:12,940
how I feel about you.

76
00:08:55,520 --> 00:08:56,520
Hold it.

77
00:08:59,130 --> 00:09:00,400
Have you had too much to drink?

78
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:07,340
Gosh, you're such a green flag,

79
00:09:07,650 --> 00:09:08,850
a very bright green at that.

80
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,590
He even asked for consent
before kissing me.

81
00:09:13,650 --> 00:09:14,320
Wait.

82
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,540
A kiss!

83
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:26,080
Dawn is fast approaching, you see.

84
00:09:26,980 --> 00:09:28,030
I think...

85
00:09:29,190 --> 00:09:30,680
I should hit the hay now

86
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:32,640
or I'll be too tired

87
00:09:33,760 --> 00:09:35,280
for tomorrow's festivities.

88
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:37,560
Klao,

89
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,360
are you displeased with me?

90
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:42,220
No.

91
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,000
I'm pleased with you,

92
00:09:44,340 --> 00:09:45,640
I really am,

93
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:46,960
but...

94
00:09:47,190 --> 00:09:49,120
I'm getting really sleepy.

95
00:09:52,780 --> 00:09:55,480
I'd better go to sleep.

96
00:09:55,980 --> 00:09:57,440
Goodnight and no dreams, Phop.

97
00:10:11,730 --> 00:10:12,640
That was close.

98
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,360
Too close.

99
00:10:15,020 --> 00:10:17,360
Things almost escalated.

100
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:22,720
Fortunately,

101
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,210
nobody saw us.

102
00:10:24,780 --> 00:10:25,660
Or

103
00:10:25,970 --> 00:10:28,280
I would've been flustered
even into my next life.

104
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,920
But why just a kiss on the cheek?

105
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,600
Is it because he still loves the real Klao?

106
00:10:51,480 --> 00:10:52,240
No.

107
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:55,750
It's like that famous period drama
that just came out.

108
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:58,280
Mom says Thais usually
didn't kiss on the lips.

109
00:10:58,910 --> 00:11:00,640
That's what Westerners do.

110
00:11:03,740 --> 00:11:04,920
This means...

111
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:07,000
he actually loves me?

112
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,520
His gaze...

113
00:11:10,950 --> 00:11:11,960
His voice...

114
00:11:12,860 --> 00:11:13,640
A kiss.

115
00:11:14,400 --> 00:11:15,840
And tomorrow, we're going on a date.

116
00:11:16,630 --> 00:11:18,520
So people in the past can be this romantic?

117
00:11:19,100 --> 00:11:21,310
This place isn't that bad after all, is it?

118
00:11:22,770 --> 00:11:23,640
You fool!

119
00:11:23,930 --> 00:11:24,750
Nakun!

120
00:11:25,050 --> 00:11:26,880
You can't stay here because of him.

121
00:11:27,250 --> 00:11:28,500
You have classes to attend.

122
00:11:28,800 --> 00:11:29,800
Thee is waiting for you.

123
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:30,920
So is Pun.

124
00:11:31,380 --> 00:11:32,120
And...

125
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:34,200
Mom.

126
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:40,880
Whoa.

127
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:42,760
This many dishes?

128
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:45,440
You want me to get full
until the next semester?

129
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:46,800
So extra.

130
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:49,890
You've been away from home
for this long,

131
00:11:49,920 --> 00:11:51,960
so it's only fair I make it up to you, no?

132
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:53,540
Go ahead and dig in.

133
00:11:57,230 --> 00:11:58,120
This is enough for me.

134
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,920
Hey! Wait!

135
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:02,720
What are you doing?

136
00:12:03,430 --> 00:12:04,280
There!

137
00:12:04,620 --> 00:12:06,440
Have some more.

138
00:12:06,470 --> 00:12:07,480
Mom...

139
00:12:08,340 --> 00:12:10,640
Eat a lot of rice, okay?

140
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:13,200
You only eat the main dishes.
Look at you.

141
00:12:14,830 --> 00:12:16,220
You're all skin and bones.

142
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:17,520
Eat up, okay?

143
00:12:17,830 --> 00:12:19,480
I'm not that skinny, Mom.

144
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,190
Come on, try this one.

145
00:12:23,220 --> 00:12:23,920
Mm.

146
00:12:31,220 --> 00:12:32,430
Mm! Tasty.

147
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:36,260
You cooked this much food for me...

148
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:38,250
You miss me, don't you?

149
00:12:57,540 --> 00:13:00,080
Me being away...

150
00:13:02,180 --> 00:13:03,280
makes you feel lonely, doesn't it?

151
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,810
What do you mean?

152
00:13:05,110 --> 00:13:07,560
I have a lot of friends, alright?

153
00:13:07,710 --> 00:13:10,570
When I get bored,
I just hang out at my friends' places.

154
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:11,480
It's fine.

155
00:13:22,100 --> 00:13:22,940
But...

156
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:26,880
I can't thank you enough

157
00:13:28,050 --> 00:13:29,800
for allowing me to study in Bangkok

158
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:36,640
after raising me all by yourself.

159
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:40,360
You've been both
a father and a mother to me,

160
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:42,600
yet you've never left me feeling lonely.

161
00:13:44,790 --> 00:13:46,070
Honestly,

162
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:49,220
if you want to be with someone else,

163
00:13:50,220 --> 00:13:51,740
I won't mind at all.

164
00:13:53,260 --> 00:13:53,880
Gosh!

165
00:13:54,160 --> 00:13:55,360
I won't.

166
00:13:55,740 --> 00:13:57,320
That only gives me a headache.

167
00:13:57,430 --> 00:14:00,120
Having you is all I need.

168
00:14:03,440 --> 00:14:04,240
But...

169
00:14:06,030 --> 00:14:07,530
I'm not always

170
00:14:08,040 --> 00:14:09,500
by your side, you know?

171
00:14:10,730 --> 00:14:11,400
You see,

172
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:13,810
after being here for about a month,

173
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:15,520
I'll have to leave
when the next month comes around.

174
00:14:15,850 --> 00:14:18,340
If I'm busy during any of my school breaks,

175
00:14:18,490 --> 00:14:19,840
I won't be able to come home to see you.

176
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:22,440
How would that make you feel?

177
00:14:25,540 --> 00:14:27,900
Listen. I'll be fine.

178
00:14:29,250 --> 00:14:32,320
Just call me if you can't make it.

179
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,610
Video calling is a thing, you know?

180
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:36,290
It's been around for ages.

181
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,960
Just video call me, for goodness' sake.

182
00:14:39,850 --> 00:14:40,560
Nakun.

183
00:14:41,600 --> 00:14:42,640
Honestly,

184
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,720
I'll be fine. Don't worry about me.

185
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:47,380
You're all grown up now.

186
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:50,540
Soon, you'll find yourself a partner.

187
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:55,950
Wait... don't tell me you already have one.

188
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:57,560
- Do you have one?
- Gosh, I don't!

189
00:14:58,610 --> 00:14:59,880
That only gives me a headache.

190
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:02,280
Having you is all I need.

191
00:15:02,650 --> 00:15:03,430
Sure.

192
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:08,040
Nakun.

193
00:15:10,340 --> 00:15:12,120
I'm serious, though.

194
00:15:13,670 --> 00:15:16,880
I want you to go out and spread your wings.

195
00:15:18,240 --> 00:15:19,670
Young adulthood

196
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:21,510
doesn't last as long as you think.

197
00:15:23,030 --> 00:15:27,160
If you come across something good in life,
do seize it, okay?

198
00:15:30,350 --> 00:15:31,960
Even if Mom said so...

199
00:15:32,670 --> 00:15:34,050
If that's the case,

200
00:15:34,380 --> 00:15:35,760
I guess I'll have to stay here

201
00:15:36,570 --> 00:15:37,780
without her.

202
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:40,600
If I want to complete my mission,

203
00:15:41,270 --> 00:15:42,620
I'll have to go home

204
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:44,600
and leave Phop behind.

205
00:15:49,710 --> 00:15:51,260
Even though I love him,

206
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:54,120
it's simply impossible, isn't it?

207
00:16:11,400 --> 00:16:14,250
I regret that I have let
so much time slip away like this.

208
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,760
I ought not to have fallen for you...

209
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:00,340
I regret having been so harsh toward Kaew.

210
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:22,050
Come on, Nakun! You shouldn't have let
your feelings get involved.

211
00:18:23,850 --> 00:18:25,360
- Did Kaew send you to speak with me?
- I seek only your advice.

212
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:54,130
- What other advice...
- Do you still not speak to him?

213
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,160
What other advice are you seeking?

214
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,160
Is there anyone who is unwell?

215
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:21,660
No.

216
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:24,600
I simply wonder

217
00:19:25,670 --> 00:19:26,280
how people

218
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:29,520
go about courting another.

219
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:02,440
Klao, the one from our childhood?

220
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:03,780
Phop!

221
00:20:07,530 --> 00:20:08,920
Are you drawn to men?

222
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:12,260
Is it that odd?

223
00:20:13,810 --> 00:20:15,720
Are you not the same, or am I mistaken?

224
00:20:21,470 --> 00:20:22,640
It is simply impossible.

225
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:23,800
Phop.

226
00:20:25,710 --> 00:20:28,250
The whole capital
will surely be abuzz with gossip over this.

227
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:29,400
Then so be it.

228
00:20:29,950 --> 00:20:32,240
I have made my choice.
My heart has belonged to Klao

229
00:20:32,960 --> 00:20:35,240
from the very beginning until now.

230
00:20:35,890 --> 00:20:38,440
I will pursue him until he is with me.

231
00:20:41,330 --> 00:20:42,780
Pray tell me, my good Physician,

232
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,480
what ought I to do?

233
00:21:00,530 --> 00:21:02,200
If that is your unwavering resolve,

234
00:21:03,050 --> 00:21:04,600
it is not my place to interfere.

235
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:09,000
Listen to me carefully, my friend.

236
00:21:12,230 --> 00:21:14,320
Before you pursue anyone's affection,

237
00:21:14,540 --> 00:21:17,640
you must be certain their heart is free.

238
00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:22,050
Acting in haste to pursue
someone already taken

239
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:25,440
will only hinder your prospects.

240
00:21:33,650 --> 00:21:34,560
What is it you are writing there?

241
00:21:45,900 --> 00:21:48,520
Why have you not yet changed
for the temple festival?

242
00:21:49,610 --> 00:21:50,310
I...

243
00:22:00,530 --> 00:22:02,320
What would give it away?

244
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:07,770
If he blushes or smiles
when you are near or when you speak,

245
00:22:07,800 --> 00:22:09,350
his heart inclines toward you.

246
00:22:12,130 --> 00:22:13,360
I'm simply...

247
00:22:13,580 --> 00:22:17,040
going over the Khmer and Pali I've learned.

248
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:19,060
But since I have amnesia,

249
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:20,920
I haven't translated anything yet.

250
00:22:24,900 --> 00:22:27,460
Once certain of their affection,

251
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:31,670
inquire after their well-being
and offer your help.

252
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:32,710
"Vihara:

253
00:22:33,610 --> 00:22:34,680
a temple

254
00:22:35,670 --> 00:22:37,160
or an ordination hall."

255
00:22:38,980 --> 00:22:40,240
"Punnotok:

256
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,020
a well-supplied

257
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:43,760
or abundant body of water,

258
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,800
such as

259
00:22:47,630 --> 00:22:49,320
a pool or a pond."

260
00:22:58,990 --> 00:23:00,210
The second period,

261
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:01,470
a pond,

262
00:23:01,500 --> 00:23:02,320
and a temple.

263
00:23:02,700 --> 00:23:03,500
Maybe it's...

264
00:23:15,050 --> 00:23:16,730
Your heart betrays you.

265
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:18,810
Does my presence stir such feelings?

266
00:23:20,520 --> 00:23:21,360
No.

267
00:23:23,660 --> 00:23:24,600
Oh, Phop.

268
00:23:24,810 --> 00:23:26,200
The temple we're visiting...

269
00:23:27,060 --> 00:23:28,640
is there a pond close to it?

270
00:23:29,780 --> 00:23:31,200
There may be no pond at that temple,

271
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,720
but the temples in the capital

272
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:36,900
all stand by the water.

273
00:23:50,200 --> 00:23:51,000
Let us go.

274
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,760
I shall change my attire first.

275
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:01,840
Go on ahead
and wait for me by the dock.

276
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:18,460
Jom's advice proves most effective.

277
00:24:18,610 --> 00:24:20,800
Klao has expressed a wish to accompany me.

278
00:24:28,810 --> 00:24:29,730
Maybe...

279
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:32,440
the body of water by the temple
in the second period

280
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:34,680
was Klao's rendezvous point.

281
00:24:34,710 --> 00:24:36,120
And then he was murdered there.

282
00:24:58,180 --> 00:25:00,200
Though there's a pier,

283
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,400
there isn't a pond
or any other body of water.

284
00:25:03,280 --> 00:25:04,760
If it were just an ordinary canal,

285
00:25:05,180 --> 00:25:08,040
Klao wouldn't have noted it down
in other languages, would he?

286
00:25:15,010 --> 00:25:16,210
Sai, would you like to try that?

287
00:25:16,260 --> 00:25:19,010
Kong, why must you
concern yourself so with my wife?

288
00:25:19,290 --> 00:25:19,980
Sai.

289
00:25:20,020 --> 00:25:21,940
Kong! Keep away from my wife.

290
00:25:21,970 --> 00:25:22,770
Chuay.

291
00:25:24,060 --> 00:25:26,050
You may wander wherever you wish.

292
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:28,840
We shall meet again
before the ordination hall.

293
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:30,840
I thank you, my Lord.

294
00:25:30,870 --> 00:25:31,550
Yes, my Lord.

295
00:25:31,580 --> 00:25:32,360
Sai.

296
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:34,650
Come, let us build a sand pagoda yonder,

297
00:25:34,930 --> 00:25:36,000
that in the next life

298
00:25:36,270 --> 00:25:38,560
we may be united again as husband and wife.

299
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:41,320
You need only build half the pagoda, Sai.

300
00:25:41,620 --> 00:25:43,720
Leave the rest for me in the next life.

301
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:46,570
How does that sound?

302
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:47,360
Kong!

303
00:25:47,740 --> 00:25:48,480
She is my wife.

304
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:49,590
I shall go with her.

305
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:50,840
Sai, wait for me.

306
00:25:59,010 --> 00:25:59,680
Klao.

307
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:02,440
What is the matter?

308
00:26:02,890 --> 00:26:03,960
Have you a fever again?

309
00:26:06,410 --> 00:26:07,060
No.

310
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:09,460
It's a bit hot here.

311
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,830
Let me go and look around real quick.

312
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:22,780
You.

313
00:26:22,810 --> 00:26:26,040
I heard you had disappeared,
and yet here you are returned?

314
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:28,120
Oh, yes.

315
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:30,560
I'm now living together with Phop.

316
00:26:37,360 --> 00:26:38,040
Klao...

317
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,880
Only say that you are living with me.

318
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:43,840
Living together means something else.

319
00:26:51,110 --> 00:26:52,640
I'll take one of these.

320
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,000
Understood.

321
00:26:56,480 --> 00:26:57,720
Here it is.

322
00:27:00,800 --> 00:27:01,880
Thank you kindly.

323
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:11,840
Come, come.

324
00:27:12,170 --> 00:27:13,030
Come here.

325
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:14,640
You come here as well.

326
00:27:14,790 --> 00:27:15,640
Goodness!

327
00:27:16,140 --> 00:27:19,160
Look yonder; that man is with another.

328
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:20,360
This is a belt

329
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:22,240
of genuine silver.

330
00:27:24,770 --> 00:27:26,060
Do come again.

331
00:27:29,050 --> 00:27:30,160
Pray, look around as you wish.

332
00:27:34,950 --> 00:27:36,070
What more is there to be done?

333
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:38,140
I have shown my care

334
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:39,990
and offered my assistance.

335
00:27:40,020 --> 00:27:41,080
What is left?

336
00:27:41,730 --> 00:27:44,590
In the courtship of a lady,

337
00:27:44,620 --> 00:27:46,360
one gives flowers or ornaments.

338
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:50,010
With Klao, it is no different.

339
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:53,040
Learn what he likes and simply buy it for him.

340
00:27:57,330 --> 00:27:58,280
Do you like it?

341
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:01,800
Of course.

342
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:05,000
But I think it's very expensive.

343
00:28:05,810 --> 00:28:06,880
I can't afford it.

344
00:28:09,620 --> 00:28:10,960
Might he try this on?

345
00:28:11,040 --> 00:28:12,660
Ah, yes, of course.

346
00:29:10,310 --> 00:29:11,220
It's beautiful.

347
00:29:12,650 --> 00:29:13,940
It's more gorgeous than CARTIER's.

348
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:19,800
If it pleases you, I shall buy it for you.

349
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:34,280
I'll save up some money
and come back for it later.

350
00:29:34,760 --> 00:29:36,680
Thank you very much, kind merchant.

351
00:29:51,460 --> 00:29:53,680
One day, I shall place this ring

352
00:29:54,580 --> 00:29:56,040
upon your finger, Klao.

353
00:30:02,940 --> 00:30:03,760
It is true.

354
00:30:04,090 --> 00:30:05,400
I saw it with my own eyes.

355
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,680
Last night,
he came out of Lord Phop's room.

356
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:10,430
This morning,
I saw them embracing by the dock.

357
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:12,360
And by afternoon,

358
00:30:12,470 --> 00:30:14,200
Lord Phop went again to Master Klao's room.

359
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:18,120
So what of it?

360
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:20,560
They have long been childhood friends.

361
00:30:21,100 --> 00:30:23,240
Sai, this is something
beyond mere friendship.

362
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,960
Are you suggesting that

363
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:29,280
my master and yours
are in a romantic affair,

364
00:30:29,310 --> 00:30:30,060
- Chuay?
- Goodness.

365
00:30:30,520 --> 00:30:32,330
How could you say such a thing, Kong?

366
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,760
Alas.

367
00:30:37,860 --> 00:30:39,870
Kong, are you so hungry that

368
00:30:40,140 --> 00:30:41,750
you would eat dirt and sand?

369
00:30:42,090 --> 00:30:44,370
I would have prepared something for you,
had you said so.

370
00:30:50,650 --> 00:30:52,460
Maybe there's a pond outside
the temple's vicinity.

371
00:30:53,100 --> 00:30:54,200
What do I do?

372
00:30:54,780 --> 00:30:56,120
How do I go out to look for one?

373
00:30:58,800 --> 00:30:59,640
Klao!

374
00:31:01,710 --> 00:31:02,560
Klao.

375
00:31:04,170 --> 00:31:05,060
How peculiar.

376
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:08,000
Last night, you were so eager
to come to the festival.

377
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:11,670
Now that we are here,
why do you seem so indifferent?

378
00:31:18,800 --> 00:31:20,080
What is it that you seek?

379
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:23,750
Nothing, actually.

380
00:31:23,930 --> 00:31:25,240
My body's just killing me.

381
00:31:33,590 --> 00:31:34,640
If so,

382
00:31:35,350 --> 00:31:37,920
shall we go and watch
the poetry and Choi chanting first?

383
00:31:39,660 --> 00:31:40,960
Since we are here,

384
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:43,890
it is best we amuse ourselves

385
00:31:45,110 --> 00:31:46,800
so that you may sleep soundly.

386
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:57,640
♫Songkran, it is♫

387
00:31:57,670 --> 00:31:59,910
♫The festival of joy♫

388
00:31:59,940 --> 00:32:03,970
♫Gather around, a most auspicious sign♫

389
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:08,360
♫This family is of great charm♫

390
00:32:09,050 --> 00:32:10,460
My Lord, this way.

391
00:32:10,770 --> 00:32:12,760
♫With a beautiful daughter♫

392
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:17,320
♫I wish to be your son-in-law,
and court her♫

393
00:32:17,350 --> 00:32:21,270
♫You are the fairest of them all♫

394
00:32:21,300 --> 00:32:25,260
♫Like the moon and stars,
I stand in awe♫

395
00:32:25,290 --> 00:32:29,470
♫So many lovely souls,
yet I am made to fall♫

396
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:32,800
Uh, we're here.

397
00:32:33,740 --> 00:32:35,480
Can you now let go of my hand?

398
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:40,250
Lastly, tease him a little and see

399
00:32:40,280 --> 00:32:43,900
if he shows any sign of shyness or blush.

400
00:32:44,180 --> 00:32:45,120
Forgive me.

401
00:32:46,350 --> 00:32:48,010
Your hand is soft.

402
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:49,960
I forgot I was holding it.

403
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:52,360
I do not wish to let it go.

404
00:32:53,800 --> 00:32:57,890
♫I broke my back
preparing dishes in the morning♫

405
00:32:57,920 --> 00:33:02,770
♫And I shall taste them,
then call you to the meal♫

406
00:33:13,210 --> 00:33:17,960
♫I shall find a woman for my son to wed,♫

407
00:33:17,990 --> 00:33:21,920
♫For he is burdened with sins
that cannot be saved♫

408
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:22,750
Mother!

409
00:33:22,920 --> 00:33:25,880
♫Cannot be saved♫

410
00:33:25,910 --> 00:33:29,770
♫We are fair and virtuous♫

411
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:34,220
♫We are virtuous and fair♫

412
00:33:34,260 --> 00:33:38,880
♫In your eyes, I find myself undone♫

413
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:44,550
♫I am captivated by your grace and charm♫

414
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:48,390
♫Your great charm I long to behold♫

415
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:52,440
♫And I wish to be close, held in your arms♫

416
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:56,340
♫Held in your arms♫

417
00:33:56,370 --> 00:34:00,080
♫Here you stand, a lonely loner♫

418
00:34:00,340 --> 00:34:04,520
♫Here you stand, a lonely loner...♫

419
00:34:04,580 --> 00:34:08,520
♫Why are you without your lover, I wonder?♫

420
00:34:08,550 --> 00:34:09,409
Goodness.

421
00:34:09,460 --> 00:34:11,920
♫I wonder if his wife...♫

422
00:34:12,510 --> 00:34:16,159
♫I wonder if his wife is so charming♫

423
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:18,219
♫That she is all worth keeping♫

424
00:34:18,250 --> 00:34:22,210
♫Or are you afraid
that she will be claimed by the dogs?♫

425
00:34:22,260 --> 00:34:23,260
I am a person.

426
00:34:23,360 --> 00:34:26,159
♫She will be claimed by the dogs♫

427
00:34:26,190 --> 00:34:30,420
♫If you are taken,
then your lady should also be here♫

428
00:34:30,760 --> 00:34:34,239
♫Your lady should also be here♫

429
00:34:34,270 --> 00:34:38,690
♫But she is not here,
so why not have me, my dear♫

430
00:34:50,500 --> 00:34:54,440
♫If you are taken,
then your lady should also be here♫

431
00:34:57,220 --> 00:34:59,730
I need to use the privy.

432
00:35:00,850 --> 00:35:02,050
I'll be right back.

433
00:35:02,260 --> 00:35:03,640
No need to follow me.

434
00:35:19,870 --> 00:35:22,300
It'd be nice if this were the modern day,

435
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,880
but this is Ayutthaya we're talking about.

436
00:35:26,070 --> 00:35:27,360
Even if we were lovers,

437
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,600
would it be socially acceptable?

438
00:35:44,610 --> 00:35:45,610
I'll let go of this love.

439
00:35:46,090 --> 00:35:46,990
It's the right thing to do.

440
00:35:47,870 --> 00:35:49,050
Focus on the mission.

441
00:35:49,700 --> 00:35:51,450
Find that pond.

442
00:36:25,510 --> 00:36:26,180
Phop.

443
00:36:28,940 --> 00:36:29,720
Cherd!

444
00:36:32,270 --> 00:36:33,850
You need not crowd me so.

445
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,260
I am not interested in being your lover,

446
00:36:35,560 --> 00:36:36,400
Klao.

447
00:36:38,040 --> 00:36:39,480
What the hell are you on about, Cherd?

448
00:36:42,330 --> 00:36:44,840
Are you pretending not to know,
or have you not heard the rumors?

449
00:36:46,540 --> 00:36:50,320
There are rumors everywhere that you
and Lord Phop are engaged in an illicit affair.

450
00:36:50,930 --> 00:36:52,360
Truly shameless.

451
00:36:55,610 --> 00:36:57,400
Why must you be so angry, Klao?

452
00:37:00,730 --> 00:37:03,360
Or is it that you are agitated
because the rumor is true?

453
00:37:14,980 --> 00:37:17,320
It is one thing for you
to be involved with Lord Phop,

454
00:37:17,600 --> 00:37:19,520
but why must you
meddle with my Pim as well?

455
00:37:21,040 --> 00:37:21,680
There!

456
00:37:26,970 --> 00:37:28,320
Hold it right there, Cherd.

457
00:37:30,960 --> 00:37:33,280
I don't see Phop in that light.

458
00:37:46,340 --> 00:37:47,480
Begone from my sight!

459
00:37:56,270 --> 00:37:58,520
Going about drawing your sword
upon the common folk,

460
00:37:59,330 --> 00:38:01,470
is this not an abuse of your authority?

461
00:38:02,280 --> 00:38:04,880
Anyone can tell who started this.

462
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,170
If you wish for no trouble,

463
00:38:07,200 --> 00:38:08,280
begone from my sight.

464
00:38:09,990 --> 00:38:11,960
This is my final warning to you.

465
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:22,960
Are you well?

466
00:38:23,200 --> 00:38:24,270
Do not meddle with me.

467
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:38,840
Phop.

468
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:41,050
I didn't mean to say that.

469
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:48,030
I know.

470
00:38:49,910 --> 00:38:50,960
Let it be so.

471
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:53,600
It is a relief to see you safe.

472
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:57,400
Why is he...

473
00:38:58,060 --> 00:38:59,440
so nice to me?

474
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:16,560
Your lips are bloodied.

475
00:39:23,080 --> 00:39:24,310
Have you injured your hand?

476
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:45,710
Ow!

477
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:47,650
Ouch!!

478
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:49,230
Ow!

479
00:39:50,180 --> 00:39:50,760
Ouch!!

480
00:39:51,570 --> 00:39:52,320
Ouch!!!

481
00:39:56,850 --> 00:39:57,600
Who are you looking for?

482
00:39:57,970 --> 00:39:58,680
No one.

483
00:39:59,810 --> 00:40:00,920
Oh, you.

484
00:40:01,230 --> 00:40:03,410
They say you have changed,
as though you were another person,

485
00:40:04,810 --> 00:40:07,030
yet you still get into fights
as you did before.

486
00:40:09,890 --> 00:40:11,030
Don't change the topic.

487
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,520
Kaew isn't coming.

488
00:40:22,350 --> 00:40:23,600
Many thanks to you.

489
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:27,400
You must be well used to courting others.

490
00:40:27,810 --> 00:40:28,520
No.

491
00:40:29,670 --> 00:40:30,700
I simply...

492
00:40:34,370 --> 00:40:35,840
Ever inquiring after their well-being.

493
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,580
Have there been many patients this day?

494
00:40:38,610 --> 00:40:40,200
Are you wearied, Jom?

495
00:40:40,690 --> 00:40:42,200
Alas.

496
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:43,440
Blood...

497
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,690
Offering your assistance.

498
00:40:49,900 --> 00:40:52,810
Learn what he likes
and simply buy it for him.

499
00:40:53,930 --> 00:40:56,880
I prepared your favorite meal,
hoping we might move past this...

500
00:40:58,160 --> 00:40:59,730
Tease him a little and see

501
00:40:59,760 --> 00:41:03,000
if he shows any sign of shyness or blush.

502
00:41:06,450 --> 00:41:08,080
I merely went by what I have seen.

503
00:41:09,940 --> 00:41:12,520
Is it because
Kaew has done likewise to you?

504
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:16,480
That is why you know so well that it works.

505
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:19,480
Speak not of such things again.

506
00:41:20,110 --> 00:41:21,880
I bear no feelings for him whatsoever.

507
00:41:36,490 --> 00:41:38,040
I know you're worried about him.

508
00:41:38,870 --> 00:41:40,440
You two had a fight yesterday, didn't you?

509
00:41:49,450 --> 00:41:51,160
We're childhood friends, alright?

510
00:41:51,740 --> 00:41:53,000
Say whatever's on your mind.

511
00:41:53,370 --> 00:41:54,640
So we can work out

512
00:41:54,950 --> 00:41:56,480
a solution for Kaew.

513
00:41:59,640 --> 00:42:00,760
It is of no consequence.

514
00:42:02,280 --> 00:42:03,560
I merely rebuked him

515
00:42:03,900 --> 00:42:06,200
for behaving so effeminately,
unbefitting a man.

516
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,860
Kaew was so furious with me
that he cursed me,

517
00:42:09,890 --> 00:42:12,240
vowing never to look upon me again
even in the next life.

518
00:42:13,820 --> 00:42:16,280
Do you believe in multiple lifetimes, Pun?

519
00:42:16,450 --> 00:42:17,400
I guess I do.

520
00:42:17,610 --> 00:42:20,880
Perhaps our paths
might have crossed in past lives.

521
00:42:21,130 --> 00:42:22,000
Then, I don't believe in it.

522
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:24,650
This lifetime is more than enough.

523
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:31,680
But it is for the best.

524
00:42:32,640 --> 00:42:34,240
Thus, he will no longer come to trouble me.

525
00:42:36,690 --> 00:42:37,720
Are you sure that's a good thing?

526
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:41,740
If you really didn't want him
to bother you,

527
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,760
you wouldn't be looking for him like this.

528
00:42:47,110 --> 00:42:48,920
Letting this go on for a day
is already bad.

529
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:51,430
Don't let this go unresolved

530
00:42:51,750 --> 00:42:53,220
into the next life.

531
00:43:12,700 --> 00:43:14,400
Apply the ointment twice daily
after bathing, Kaew.

532
00:43:17,820 --> 00:43:18,560
Klao.

533
00:43:21,780 --> 00:43:22,560
See?

534
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:25,280
You miss him, don't you?

535
00:43:25,650 --> 00:43:27,520
Don't deny what your heart tells you.

536
00:43:30,520 --> 00:43:31,480
I know that

537
00:43:31,950 --> 00:43:32,720
you...

538
00:43:33,770 --> 00:43:36,520
You're afraid of being judged by others.

539
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:39,260
But those who gossip

540
00:43:40,010 --> 00:43:41,480
don't share your sorrow, you see.

541
00:43:44,750 --> 00:43:45,880
Our loved ones

542
00:43:46,290 --> 00:43:47,240
are the most important thing.

543
00:43:48,960 --> 00:43:50,740
If Kaew were heartbroken

544
00:43:50,910 --> 00:43:51,990
and ended his life right now,

545
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:53,240
what would you do?

546
00:44:17,180 --> 00:44:17,870
Master Klao,

547
00:44:17,900 --> 00:44:20,120
allow me to prepare
jasmine-scented water for you.

548
00:44:29,270 --> 00:44:29,960
Phop.

549
00:44:30,750 --> 00:44:32,400
I would like to apologize to you again

550
00:44:33,160 --> 00:44:36,080
for saying those things
while I was fighting with Cherd.

551
00:44:37,920 --> 00:44:41,240
I just don't want anyone
to gossip about you.

552
00:44:42,470 --> 00:44:43,470
I know.

553
00:44:44,160 --> 00:44:46,030
But you yourself said that

554
00:44:46,650 --> 00:44:49,130
those who gossip
do not share in our sorrow.

555
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:58,760
If you care for no one,

556
00:44:59,540 --> 00:45:01,670
would you tell me

557
00:45:02,190 --> 00:45:04,120
how you feel about me?

558
00:45:14,640 --> 00:45:15,570
Master Klao!

559
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:17,080
Master!!

560
00:45:17,460 --> 00:45:18,400
Master Klao.

561
00:45:18,890 --> 00:45:20,100
His Excellency has summoned you.

562
00:45:21,460 --> 00:45:22,960
Does he summon only Dear Klao?

563
00:45:24,330 --> 00:45:25,520
What of me?

564
00:45:25,690 --> 00:45:27,880
You have something
to discuss with me, Lord Phop.

565
00:45:41,410 --> 00:45:43,920
High Lord Soontrapinit came here to see me

566
00:45:46,020 --> 00:45:48,400
to discuss Phop and Lady Varna.

567
00:45:56,350 --> 00:45:58,070
Is it concerning marriage, Your Excellency?

568
00:46:00,450 --> 00:46:01,160
Yes.

569
00:46:03,360 --> 00:46:05,960
Harn serves in
the patrol department as Phop.

570
00:46:06,600 --> 00:46:08,480
The High Lord holds a high rank,

571
00:46:08,510 --> 00:46:10,800
which may open the way for you
to enter royal service.

572
00:46:11,440 --> 00:46:13,200
As for Lady Varna,

573
00:46:13,730 --> 00:46:15,400
she is flawless in every way.

574
00:46:16,870 --> 00:46:18,440
Do you not agree?

575
00:46:22,380 --> 00:46:23,240
Yes.

576
00:46:24,270 --> 00:46:25,880
Yet Phop continues to evade the matter,

577
00:46:26,660 --> 00:46:28,600
never allowing me to formally ask her.

578
00:46:30,000 --> 00:46:31,520
You are close to Phop.

579
00:46:32,360 --> 00:46:33,440
Do you know

580
00:46:33,740 --> 00:46:36,360
if he has set his sights upon anyone else?

581
00:46:42,870 --> 00:46:44,150
I...

582
00:46:46,280 --> 00:46:47,440
It would seem he does not.

583
00:46:49,090 --> 00:46:49,840
Good.

584
00:46:51,260 --> 00:46:54,080
To let her frequent this house so often

585
00:46:54,660 --> 00:46:57,040
will only lead to gossip and scandal.

586
00:46:58,250 --> 00:46:59,760
Even High Lord Soontrapinit

587
00:47:00,260 --> 00:47:01,520
is far from being at ease with this.

588
00:47:06,110 --> 00:47:08,800
I pray you speak with Phop on my behalf.

589
00:47:11,330 --> 00:47:14,300
I wish to see my son settled

590
00:47:15,090 --> 00:47:17,040
before I no longer have the chance.

591
00:47:23,570 --> 00:47:24,360
Yes, Your Excellency.

592
00:47:45,750 --> 00:47:47,600
The soldiers have captured the smugglers

593
00:47:47,630 --> 00:47:50,200
who carried opium
from the capital to sell in Sam Khok.

594
00:47:51,460 --> 00:47:53,480
My father conducted the interrogation himself,

595
00:47:55,140 --> 00:47:57,120
yet none of them would confess.

596
00:47:58,940 --> 00:48:01,560
The market district under your supervision

597
00:48:02,080 --> 00:48:04,000
also has many opium smokers, does it not?

598
00:48:07,980 --> 00:48:08,600
Yes.

599
00:48:12,080 --> 00:48:14,440
And Klao shall return there
once more, I do reckon.

600
00:48:17,170 --> 00:48:17,840
Lord Phop,

601
00:48:19,400 --> 00:48:21,040
did you know that just before the New Year,

602
00:48:22,200 --> 00:48:25,080
Klao went to visit
a prostitute by the name of Pim?

603
00:48:26,060 --> 00:48:27,990
He ended up in a brawl with Cherd.

604
00:48:30,720 --> 00:48:33,640
The locals are abuzz with rumors
that they are fighting over her.

605
00:48:35,390 --> 00:48:37,000
It would seem your brother

606
00:48:37,180 --> 00:48:39,680
has truly fallen in love with
the young lady,

607
00:48:40,650 --> 00:48:43,120
beyond mere physical desire, Lord Phop.

608
00:48:50,640 --> 00:48:51,410
My Lord!

609
00:48:51,440 --> 00:48:52,440
My Lord!!

610
00:48:52,920 --> 00:48:53,680
My Lord.

611
00:48:55,100 --> 00:48:56,520
Master Klao is missing.

612
00:48:57,650 --> 00:48:58,520
How so?

613
00:48:58,910 --> 00:49:00,080
When did he go missing?

614
00:49:00,550 --> 00:49:01,800
I am not certain, my Lord.

615
00:49:02,030 --> 00:49:04,310
He was speaking with
His Excellency one moment,

616
00:49:04,340 --> 00:49:06,290
and the next,

617
00:49:06,320 --> 00:49:07,560
Master Klao was gone.

618
00:49:08,660 --> 00:49:09,680
I knew it.

619
00:49:11,100 --> 00:49:13,120
I am certain he has gone to seek out Pim.

620
00:49:15,640 --> 00:49:17,680
I am greatly concerned
for your brother, Lord Phop.

621
00:50:07,240 --> 00:50:08,060
Kaew.

622
00:50:11,530 --> 00:50:12,480
I pray you, come out.

623
00:50:15,450 --> 00:50:18,120
The servants said
you have yet to eat anything all day.

624
00:50:26,470 --> 00:50:27,160
I...

625
00:50:32,980 --> 00:50:34,720
I have brought you some of your favorites.

626
00:51:16,810 --> 00:51:17,880
Pray, just go.

627
00:51:20,210 --> 00:51:21,880
If you hold no affection for me,

628
00:51:23,340 --> 00:51:24,600
then come not near me again.

629
00:51:30,090 --> 00:51:31,920
I pray you,
come out and speak with me, Kaew.

630
00:51:34,050 --> 00:51:35,160
I am worried for you.

631
00:52:04,700 --> 00:52:05,400
No.

632
00:52:09,100 --> 00:52:10,120
Pray, leave.

633
00:52:11,330 --> 00:52:13,340
We have nothing further
to say to each other.

634
00:52:27,680 --> 00:52:28,760
I shall wait

635
00:52:32,980 --> 00:52:34,400
until your anger abates.

636
00:53:39,650 --> 00:53:41,520
Why is it that whenever I'm not at ease,

637
00:53:42,150 --> 00:53:43,560
my heart tells me to come here?

638
00:53:48,150 --> 00:53:50,000
The more I pretend to be Klao,

639
00:53:51,370 --> 00:53:53,400
the more I feel like I'm actually him.

640
00:53:56,940 --> 00:53:58,800
I knew you would be here.

641
00:54:07,040 --> 00:54:08,720
You have been gone until night has fallen.

642
00:54:10,030 --> 00:54:12,600
People believed you had gone to
the House of Pleasure again.

643
00:54:19,940 --> 00:54:21,440
Lord Harn told you that, didn't he?

644
00:54:24,390 --> 00:54:25,640
The last time,

645
00:54:26,560 --> 00:54:28,240
he met me while I was with Cherd.

646
00:54:29,880 --> 00:54:31,520
I am certain you will not return there.

647
00:54:34,440 --> 00:54:36,880
I believe I know you, my Klao, well enough.

648
00:54:57,380 --> 00:54:58,840
Is something troubling you?

649
00:55:00,370 --> 00:55:02,760
Chuay told me that
you went to speak with my father.

650
00:55:09,470 --> 00:55:10,120
I did.

651
00:55:12,000 --> 00:55:13,550
I did speak with him.

652
00:55:16,580 --> 00:55:19,680
He wants you to get married.

653
00:55:23,250 --> 00:55:25,240
He's already pretty old.

654
00:55:26,640 --> 00:55:28,160
As for you, Phop,

655
00:55:29,860 --> 00:55:31,640
you've come of age.

656
00:55:33,870 --> 00:55:35,320
If there's nothing that troubles you,

657
00:55:39,880 --> 00:55:41,360
then go ahead and tell him.

658
00:55:56,080 --> 00:55:56,840
Klao,

659
00:55:57,770 --> 00:55:59,510
if I am to be wed,

660
00:56:00,040 --> 00:56:02,040
it shall certainly not be to Lady Varna.

661
00:56:09,000 --> 00:56:11,060
I could never share my life with anyone

662
00:56:12,940 --> 00:56:14,170
but you.

663
00:56:32,640 --> 00:56:35,230
I cannot even say when it began,

664
00:56:37,280 --> 00:56:40,150
but right now,
all I know is that I wish to be with you,

665
00:56:43,790 --> 00:56:46,880
to care for you,
and to stay by your side forever.

666
00:56:56,360 --> 00:56:57,580
There is neither liquor

667
00:56:58,500 --> 00:57:00,040
nor fermented palm sugar drink here.

668
00:57:02,450 --> 00:57:04,900
Everything I am about to say to you

669
00:57:07,080 --> 00:57:08,750
comes purely from the depths of my heart.

670
00:57:14,920 --> 00:57:17,740
I no longer look upon you
as my younger brother,

671
00:57:20,760 --> 00:57:22,630
but as the man

672
00:57:27,600 --> 00:57:30,780
with whom
I wish to spend the rest of my life.

673
00:57:40,480 --> 00:57:42,330
Is that clear enough for you, Klao?

674
00:58:15,570 --> 00:58:17,620
This kiss is meant to convey
the love I hold for you.

675
00:58:20,530 --> 00:58:23,250
Let me assure you once again...

676
00:58:26,270 --> 00:58:27,320
I love you

677
00:58:28,700 --> 00:58:30,040
with all my heart.

678
00:58:34,540 --> 00:58:36,120
What do you say, Dear Klao?

679
00:58:39,040 --> 00:58:40,910
How do you feel about me?

680
00:58:47,460 --> 00:58:48,170
Phop.

681
00:58:51,100 --> 00:58:51,970
That was a kiss?

682
00:58:52,570 --> 00:58:53,570
Let me show you how it's done.

683
01:00:33,930 --> 01:00:35,200
What is the matter?

684
01:00:38,100 --> 01:00:39,480
Why are you in tears?

685
01:00:41,630 --> 01:00:43,280
You also love me, do you not?

686
01:00:46,880 --> 01:00:47,610
I do.

687
01:00:48,100 --> 01:00:48,880
Phop.

688
01:00:49,870 --> 01:00:51,040
I do love you,

689
01:00:53,290 --> 01:00:54,120
but

690
01:00:55,180 --> 01:00:57,000
love alone isn't enough.

691
01:01:13,630 --> 01:01:15,880
You're a lord.

692
01:01:17,180 --> 01:01:18,440
You're in the patrol unit.

693
01:01:20,970 --> 01:01:21,900
Just today alone,

694
01:01:23,810 --> 01:01:25,590
everyone was already staring at us.

695
01:01:27,460 --> 01:01:28,560
I care not.

696
01:01:30,280 --> 01:01:31,600
You said that...

697
01:01:31,630 --> 01:01:33,040
You should care.

698
01:01:37,700 --> 01:01:39,310
If this were the place I came from,

699
01:01:39,700 --> 01:01:41,120
I would've feared nothing.

700
01:01:43,640 --> 01:01:45,360
But here, it's different.

701
01:01:47,290 --> 01:01:48,720
How would you live your life like this?

702
01:01:57,260 --> 01:01:58,280
Let us go

703
01:01:59,800 --> 01:02:01,440
to a place where we may express our love.

704
01:02:04,950 --> 01:02:05,720
Phop.

705
01:02:07,100 --> 01:02:08,840
How would that be possible, Phop?

706
01:02:10,630 --> 01:02:11,600
What about your father?

707
01:02:13,390 --> 01:02:14,560
What about your mother?

708
01:02:16,930 --> 01:02:17,820
Regardless,

709
01:02:18,820 --> 01:02:20,890
you'll end up marrying Lady Varna.

710
01:02:22,060 --> 01:02:23,390
It's the best option.

711
01:02:30,840 --> 01:02:31,840
You...

712
01:02:34,040 --> 01:02:36,180
Do you truly wish for me
to be wed so badly?

713
01:02:41,370 --> 01:02:42,140
Yes.

714
01:02:44,780 --> 01:02:46,520
Your parents

715
01:02:47,200 --> 01:02:48,280
and I

716
01:02:49,920 --> 01:02:51,440
really wish for you to get married.

717
01:02:54,320 --> 01:02:56,200
Once you have settled down,

718
01:02:57,470 --> 01:02:59,040
I'd be extremely delighted.

719
01:03:36,570 --> 01:03:37,320
My Phop.

720
01:03:38,840 --> 01:03:39,840
I'm terribly sorry.

721
01:03:41,810 --> 01:03:43,370
♫I know too well,♫

722
01:03:43,400 --> 01:03:45,320
I pray you, let go of this love.

723
01:03:47,470 --> 01:03:49,770
It's best we're brothers.

724
01:03:53,390 --> 01:03:55,480
I beg you to understand me.

725
01:03:57,900 --> 01:04:05,760
♫I understand that everything has its time♫

726
01:04:05,850 --> 01:04:11,880
♫Through frightening distance
and wavering paths♫

727
01:04:11,910 --> 01:04:13,000
I understand.

728
01:04:13,920 --> 01:04:17,640
♫But our bond grows stronger and stronger♫

729
01:04:17,680 --> 01:04:19,310
♫How much longer will it last?♫

730
01:04:19,340 --> 01:04:23,320
♫I pray that we fall into deep slumber♫

731
01:04:23,350 --> 01:04:24,680
Your lantern has gone out.

732
01:04:26,500 --> 01:04:27,360
Come with me;

733
01:04:28,110 --> 01:04:29,360
I shall guide you.

734
01:04:43,600 --> 01:04:44,780
He's being nice again.

735
01:04:45,870 --> 01:04:48,080
Just walking away from me
wouldn't hurt me this deeply.

736
01:04:51,600 --> 01:04:53,030
If there is a next life,

737
01:04:54,080 --> 01:04:55,660
I hope we'll meet again

738
01:04:56,340 --> 01:04:58,560
in a world where men
can fall in love freely.

739
01:05:01,770 --> 01:05:06,390
♫I wish saying goodbye were just a dream♫

740
01:05:06,420 --> 01:05:12,330
♫I wish you'd return to me
when I wake from sleep♫

741
01:05:12,370 --> 01:05:17,620
♫I hope you're by my side
as I wipe away my tears♫

742
01:05:17,650 --> 01:05:22,330
♫Yet a farewell kiss
is what I'll hold so dear♫

743
01:05:22,360 --> 01:05:26,330
♫As you're now gone forever from my grasp♫

744
01:05:26,360 --> 01:05:30,150
♫Though countless lifetimes
may have passed,♫

745
01:05:30,180 --> 01:05:34,850
♫My heart will always be yours♫

746
01:05:36,320 --> 01:05:37,530
You did the right thing, Nakun.

747
01:05:38,780 --> 01:05:40,960
Even if he didn't get married
to Lady Varna...

748
01:05:42,420 --> 01:05:44,770
If he found out I wasn't the real Klao,

749
01:05:45,880 --> 01:05:47,440
he'd be in deep sorrow.

750
01:06:10,710 --> 01:06:11,710
I wonder

751
01:06:12,590 --> 01:06:14,360
how heartbroken he feels.

752
01:06:38,080 --> 01:06:39,200
Make haste.

753
01:08:01,440 --> 01:08:02,220
I...

754
01:08:03,120 --> 01:08:04,600
I offer this prayer...

755
01:08:10,740 --> 01:08:11,430
There.

756
01:08:11,870 --> 01:08:13,240
That's what Rattikarn,
the fortune teller, said.

757
01:08:14,810 --> 01:08:15,680
"Rattikarn"

758
01:08:15,970 --> 01:08:17,319
isn't just her name.

759
01:08:17,720 --> 01:08:19,160
The name means nighttime.

760
01:08:19,840 --> 01:08:20,640
Cold.

761
01:08:21,380 --> 01:08:23,359
He was suffocating
because he was weighed down underwater.

762
01:08:24,810 --> 01:08:26,680
Cherd stabbed me in a hut

763
01:08:27,700 --> 01:08:29,359
and threw me into the water.

764
01:08:41,270 --> 01:08:43,200
So this writing refers to
the incident at the hut?

765
01:08:43,670 --> 01:08:44,720
What about the temple?

766
01:08:45,399 --> 01:08:46,600
What does it mean?

767
01:08:54,410 --> 01:08:55,279
The point of reference.

768
01:08:55,490 --> 01:08:56,950
Do I enter the woods by the temple

769
01:08:57,390 --> 01:08:58,560
to find the hut?

770
01:09:04,160 --> 01:09:04,920
Which temple is it?

771
01:09:05,859 --> 01:09:07,200
Is it the same one I visited today?

772
01:09:07,939 --> 01:09:09,399
That's why Cherd and his men were waiting for me.

773
01:10:48,640 --> 01:10:49,880
Oh, Jom!

774
01:10:49,930 --> 01:10:51,880
You spent the entire night
waiting for him before his room.

775
01:10:52,060 --> 01:10:54,880
I hear that Kaew is moving to another city.

776
01:10:57,590 --> 01:10:59,680
The reason I had to get close to Cherd

777
01:10:59,710 --> 01:11:00,760
was that...

778
01:11:00,810 --> 01:11:02,400
You are suspicious of him?

779
01:11:02,610 --> 01:11:03,880
Pray tell me

780
01:11:04,020 --> 01:11:06,050
Cherd has some involvement
in the opium trade.

781
01:11:06,080 --> 01:11:07,130
My Lord!

782
01:11:07,230 --> 01:11:09,560
The patrol unit seized
sufficient opium to fill an entire cart.

783
01:11:09,820 --> 01:11:11,040
Lord Harn, there is a chance

784
01:11:11,200 --> 01:11:13,480
we may trace this back to those behind it.

785
01:11:13,600 --> 01:11:14,680
I beg of you.

786
01:11:14,710 --> 01:11:16,890
If Lord Phop discovers
we have been trailing him,

787
01:11:16,920 --> 01:11:18,310
I shall surely lose my head, Master.

788
01:11:22,040 --> 01:11:24,640
You may scold or chastise me as you will.

789
01:11:25,620 --> 01:11:27,700
I am more than relieved
that you made it out alive.

790
01:11:27,740 --> 01:11:32,300
♫I wish saying goodbye were just a dream♫

791
01:11:32,350 --> 01:11:38,180
♫I wish you'd return to me
when I wake from sleep♫

792
01:11:38,240 --> 01:11:43,790
♫I hope that you're by my side
as I wipe away my tears♫

793
01:11:43,820 --> 01:11:48,370
♫Yet a farewell kiss
is what I'll hold so dear♫

794
01:11:48,400 --> 01:11:52,240
♫As you're now gone forever from my grasp♫

795
01:11:52,270 --> 01:11:56,040
♫Though countless lifetimes
may have passed,♫

796
01:11:56,070 --> 01:12:00,590
♫My heart will always be yours♫

797
01:12:24,040 --> 01:12:28,000
[Love Upon a Time Series]
